description: Lovingly maintained south facing single family home located in the heart of South Boston. Blocks from South Boston's famous shoreline, and steps to the best of what South Boston has to offer! Minutes to the Seaport District or downtown Boston, with easy airport and highway access, and all bus routes. Living room is separate from the kitchen and dining area. Kitchen leads to spacious patio. Half bathroom is on the main floor with skylight access on second floor landing. Top floor level consists of three bedrooms plus a renovated full bathroom with full size washer and dryer. Updated lower level has full bathroom with full size washer/dryer and private street entrance.
